events.detail: The first ever blood donation from Judoh company.

events.name: Give a gift of blood
events.detail: 3 person may be saved from blood donated from 1 person.

events.name: Health and Wellbeing at work

location.address: Khoa CNTT, Đại Học Cần Thơ

events.detail: The aim is to raise global awareness of the need for safe blood and blood products for transfusion and of the critical contribution voluntary, unpaid blood donors make to national health systems.

events.name: Judoh Blood Donations
events.detail: Safe blood and blood products and their transfusion are a critical aspect of care and public health. They save millions of lives and improve the health and quality of life of many patients every day.

events.name: We are Donors
events.detail: Throughout the COVID-19 pandemic, despite limited mobility and other challenges, blood donors in many countries have continued to donate blood and plasma to patients who need transfusion.

events.name: Judoh Blood Donations - Summer Edition
events.detail: Encourage youth to embrace the humanitarian call to donate blood and inspire others to do the same

events.name: Judoh Blood Donations - Christmast Edition
